# Import format for type-only imports

Use `import type` when importing types only. Put `type` before the braces, not inside.

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD
import type { AssociateTabId } from '@/components/AssociateSidebar';
import type { Customer } from '@/types/data';

// ❌ BAD – inline type modifier
import { type AssociateTabId } from '@/components/AssociateSidebar';
import { type Customer } from '@/types/data';
```
